<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 02:07:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国众议院主要委员会正在准备立法以制定加密货币税收结构</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</link><description>负责税收政策的众议院小组正在准备立法，以解决加密货币的税收问题，最早将于周五发布，下周初将举行听证会。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQWwstahc5G8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 23:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</guid></item><item><title>不再需要比特币的区块链正在获得动力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-04/blockchain-no-longer-needing-bitcoin-is-gaining-momentum</link><description>金融科技对产品比代币价格更感兴趣。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isIkrVfDkPpc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-04/blockchain-no-longer-needing-bitcoin-is-gaining-momentum</guid></item><item><title>塞勒的比特币机器每个气缸都失火了</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-machine-is-misfiring-on-every-cylinder</link><description>Michael Saylor 围绕一个简单的想法创建了 Strategy Inc.：筹集资金购买比特币，然后永远不要出售它。随着时间的推移，这个简单的赌注变得更加复杂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2Qy.ZajUlDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 16:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-machine-is-misfiring-on-every-cylinder</guid></item><item><title>战略抛售引发溃败后，比特币与科技股的差距扩大</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</link><description>在Strategy Inc.出售其庞大加密货币库存的一小部分后，比特币的抛售一直持续到周三，这扰乱了市场情绪，并扩大了该代币与创纪录的科技股之间的差距。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaTE4QmyBCK4/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 06:25:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币的融化，180％的加密货币反弹显示了新的投资时代</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</link><description>随着数十亿美元离开比特币和以太基金，资金正在流入加密货币的一个角落，这承诺了投资者长期以来在数字资产中难以找到的东西：从经济活动到代币价值的更清晰的路径。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTOFRhQJR_aA/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</guid></item></channel></rss>